Network library and associated test programs in C++20.

This project has been tested on the following platforms:

+===========+=====================+====================+========+========+
| OS Family | Distribution        | OS Version (Port)  | GCC    | Clang  |
+===========+=====================+====================+========+========+
| GNU/Linux | Debian              | 11 (arm64)         | 10.2.1 | N/A    |
+-----------+---------------------+--------------------+--------+--------+
| GNU/Linux | Fedora              | 36 (arm64)         | 12.1.1 | 14.0.0 |
+-----------+---------------------+--------------------+--------+--------+
| GNU/Linux | openSUSE Tumbleweed | 20220530 (arm64)   | 12.1.0 | 14.0.4 |
+-----------+---------------------+--------------------+--------+--------+
| GNU/Linux | Ubuntu              | 20.04 LTS (arm64)  | 10.3.0 | N/A    |
+-----------+---------------------+--------------------+--------+--------+
| Unix      | Apple macOS         | 12.4 (arm64)       | N/A    | 14.0.6 |
+-----------+---------------------+--------------------+--------+--------+
| Windows   | Cygwin              | 10.0 (amd64)       | 11.3.0 | N/A    |
+-----------+---------------------+--------------------+--------+--------+
| Windows   | MinGW               | 10.0 (amd64)       | 12.2.0 | 14.0.6 |
+-----------+---------------------+--------------------+--------+--------+

The various OS ports have been tested on the following processors:

+===========+====================================+=========+=========+
| CPU ISA   | CPU Vendor and Microarchitecture   | 32 bit  | 64 bit  |
+===========+====================================+=========+=========+
| ARMv8.4-A | Apple M1                           | N/A     | arm64   |
+-----------+------------------------------------+---------+---------+
| x86-64    | Intel Silvermont, Kaby Lake,       | N/A     | amd64/  |
|           | and Coffee Lake                    |         | x86_64  |
+-----------+------------------------------------+---------+---------+
